               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280529-134-cd742" type="crimeDate">6th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280529-134-off741 t18280529-134-cd742"></join>, 1 candlestick, value 5s.
            </rs>, the goods of 
               <persName id="t18280529-134-victim797" type="victimName">
                  James 
